e) **SEARCH French or German Celtic studies scholarship** (Revue Celtique, Études Celtiques, publications from EPHE or Université de Rennes) for analysis of whether the TDD were understood as literal pre-human inhabitants by the medieval Irish, or as euhemerized gods.

